[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 2.12"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 2.12 are now fixed in Tails 3.0.

We **strongly** encourage you to
[[upgrade to Tails 3.0|news/version_3.0]] as soon as possible.

- Tor Browser: [[!mfsa 2017-16]]
